## Datasets

Datasets are not included in this repository due to size and licensing constraints.

1.	Structured: IEEE-CIS Fraud Detection Dataset [https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/ieee-fraud-detection/data]
2.	Unstructured: PubLayNet [ https://dax-cdn.cdn.appdomain.cloud/dax-publaynet/1.0.0/test.tar.gz  alt https://huggingface.co/datasets/lhoestq/small-publaynet-wds/tree/main] or CORD-19 [https://github.com/allenai/cord19?tab=readme-ov-file]
3.	Semi-structured: Amazon Fashion Reviews [https://amazon-reviews-2023.github.io/]
4.	Sparse: 2022 Ireland Census [https://data-osi.opendata.arcgis.com/datasets/osi::cso-small-areas-national-statistical-boundaries-2022-ungeneralised/explore]

All preprocessing and feature extraction steps are documented in the notebooks.
